        "vs_Regulation": "Balance is STATE of equilibrium; Regulation is MECHANISM of control",
        "vs_Symmetry": "Balance is equilibrium of FORCES/FLOWS; Symmetry is invariance under TRANSFORMATION",
        "vs_Constraint": "Balance is ACHIEVED state; Constraint is IMPOSED limitation"
      },
      "m2:transdisciplinaryValidation": {
