        "Cortex: stimulus → percept (neuroscience)",
        "Translator: language A → language B (linguistics)"
      ],
      "m2:distinctFrom": {
        "m2:Channel": "Channel (F⊗I⊗S) transmits without transformation — no D (temporal unfolding); Processor actively transforms",
        "m2:Mediator": "Mediator (S⊗I⊗F) connects without active transformation; Processor changes the nature of I",
        "m2:Transducer": "Transducer is a Processor specialization focused on flux-type conversion (a-temporal); Processor is the general case with D",
        "m2:Agent": "Agent (S⊗I⊗D) is an autonomous actor; Processor is a transformation component (not necessarily autonomous)"
      },
